2006-06-12  Shahzad Muzaffar  <Shahzad.Muzaffar@cern.ch>

	* interface/*, src/*, BuildFile: First implementation of generic
	visualisation application. Currently one can add something like
	service = VisConfigurationService {
	  untracked vstring Views = {'RPhi Window','RZ Window'}
	  untracked vstring Services = {'Services/Framework/GUI/', 'Services/Framework/Config Rc' }
	  untracked bool TextBrowser = 1
	  untracked bool TwigBrowser = 1
	  untracked vstring  ContentProxies = {'Cosmics/Core', 'Cosmics/Geometry', 'Cosmics/Tracks',
	                                       'Cosmics/MagField', 'Cosmics/RecHits', 'Cosmics/Digis',
					       'Reco/Hcal','Reco/Calorimetry' }
	}
	in his/her .cfg file to configure it for a sepecific application. Default values
	of the above fields are
	Views = {'3D Window" }
	Services = {'Services/Framework/GUI/'}
	TextBrowser = 1
	TwigBrowser = 1
	ContentProxies = {}
